[{"id":866324,"node":"旅行","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/travel","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/fc22/1309/181_mini.png?m=1608240651","description":"继去年秋天去过南疆之后，半月前又去了一趟北疆，当前是伊犁和独库公路最美的时候，一路风景尽收眼底。<br />只是路程确实比较长，大部分时间都耗在路上，但最美的风景也在路上。<br />从出发到返回将近 20 天，行程路线：喀纳斯-贾登峪-禾木-克拉玛依-赛里木湖-伊犁-巴音布鲁克-独库公路（北段）-天池-吐鲁番<br />算是北疆大环线，但伊犁段因为伊昭公路当时还没有开通，有些遗憾没走成，以后会再去一趟，徒步夏塔古道。<br /><br />直接上图，图片均为手机拍摄，如果你认为加了滤镜，那是拍摄时手机 AI 自动加的……实景可能更好看。<br /><img src=\"https://wx3.sinaimg.cn/large/5f18ebd8ly1h47ch6yx94j21400u0n9c.jpg\" class=\"embedded_image\" rel=\"noreferrer\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\"> <br /><img src=\"https://wx2.sinaimg.cn/large/5f18ebd8ly1h47ch9mus0j21400u049b.jpg\" class=\"embedded_image\" rel=\"noreferrer\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\"> <br /><img src=\"https://wx3.sinaimg.cn/large/5f18ebd8ly1h47chakr07j20u0140tp9.jpg\" class=\"embedded_image\" rel=\"noreferrer\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\"> <br /><img src=\"https://wx4.sinaimg.cn/large/5f18ebd8ly1h47chaximnj21400u0apw.jpg\" class=\"embedded_image\" rel=\"noreferrer\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\"> <br /><img src=\"https://wx2.sinaimg.cn/large/5f18ebd8ly1h47chcdc2fj21400u0n96.jpg\" class=\"embedded_image\" rel=\"noreferrer\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\"> <br /><img src=\"https://wx1.sinaimg.cn/large/5f18ebd8ly1h47chtgugbj21400u048s.jpg\" class=\"embedded_image\" rel=\"noreferrer\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\"> <br /><img src=\"https://wx3.sinaimg.cn/large/5f18ebd8ly1h47chq801nj21400u0qa3.jpg\" class=\"embedded_image\" rel=\"noreferrer\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\"> <br /><img src=\"https://wx4.sinaimg.cn/large/5f18ebd8ly1h47chlymzpj21400u0djo.jpg\" class=\"embedded_image\" rel=\"noreferrer\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\"> <br /><img src=\"https://wx1.sinaimg.cn/large/5f18ebd8ly1h47chb9av6j20xc0m7ajk.jpg\" class=\"embedded_image\" rel=\"noreferrer\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\"> <br /><img src=\"https://wx1.sinaimg.cn/large/5f18ebd8ly1h47chredc5j21400u07hd.jpg\" class=\"embedded_image\" rel=\"noreferrer\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\"> <br /><img src=\"https://wx1.sinaimg.cn/large/5f18ebd8ly1h47ci44mlgj21400u0an9.jpg\" class=\"embedded_image\" rel=\"noreferrer\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\"> <br /><img src=\"https://wx4.sinaimg.cn/large/5f18ebd8ly1h47chvfy25j21400u0ao1.jpg\" class=\"embedded_image\" rel=\"noreferrer\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\"> <br /><img src=\"https://wx4.sinaimg.cn/large/5f18ebd8ly1h47ci02844j21400u0h0w.jpg\" class=\"embedded_image\" rel=\"noreferrer\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\"> <br /><img src=\"https://wx2.sinaimg.cn/large/5f18ebd8ly1h47chzovb5j21400u0gqo.jpg\" class=\"embedded_image\" rel=\"noreferrer\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\"> <br /><br />以上是部分图片，详细内容和攻略-&gt;  <br /><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/92lE8n6qDYklxf8u_thv2w\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/92lE8n6qDYklxf8u_thv2w</a>","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/866324","replies":116,"created_ts":1657849717,"created":"09:48:37","title":"北疆归来~一路把眼睛喂饱！（伊犁环线+独库公路+阿勒泰）","author":"ichigo","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/ichigo","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/b4bf/5de1/17661_mini.png?m=1657848990"},{"id":866291,"node":"分享发现","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/share","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c74d/97b0/16_mini.png?m=1650127281","description":"<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-4b9aa2cf635db27e7779d2d3761dafd8_r.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">pic1.zhimg.com/v2-4b9aa2cf635db27e7779d2d3761dafd8_r.jpg</a><br /><br />以后只选择 Microsoft Office<br /><br />Office365 很香","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/866291","replies":112,"created_ts":1657840886,"created":"07:21:26","title":"WPS 锁定用户文件，之前说 WPS 够用的朋友还好吗？","author":"Eagleyes","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/Eagleyes","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/e692/1668/330833_mini.png?m=1651213904"},{"id":866413,"node":"程序员","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1656605007","description":"<p>用过一段 nodejs 的 <a href=\"https://www.prisma.io/\" rel=\"nofollow\">prisma</a>，CURD 确实很爽，但麻烦一点的查询就只能手写 SQL 了，因为 prisma 这个框架不提供底层的 query builder ，最后还是换回了 <a href=\"https://knexjs.org/\" rel=\"nofollow\">knex</a> 这个 query builder 一把梭。</p>\n<p>我想了解一下其它编程语言都有哪些好用的 ORM ，哪些 feature 让你选择这个 ORM ?</p>\n<p>听说过 laravel 的 <a href=\"https://laravel.com/docs/9.x/eloquent\" rel=\"nofollow\">Eloquent</a> 很好用，但不知道 php 现在 Type Hints 发展的怎么样，有没有像 typescript 一样被广泛应用，因为现在大部分常用的 npm 包都有官方或第三方 typescript 类型注释支持。</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/866413","replies":111,"created_ts":1657864197,"created":"13:49:57","title":"不限编程语言，你认为哪个 ORM 最好用？","author":"yodhcn","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/yodhcn","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/ac1d/d52e/504833_mini.png?m=1655535764"},{"id":866313,"node":"程序员","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1656605007","description":"","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/866313","replies":108,"created_ts":1657847804,"created":"09:16:44","title":"同事总是没事头撇过来盯着你屏幕看你在干什么。。。觉得很烦","author":"Renco","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/Renco","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/8530/7718/402540_mini.png?m=1637991602"},{"id":866300,"node":"程序员","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1656605007","description":"<p>分析报告： <a href=\"https://www.bilibili.com/read/cv17521097\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://www.bilibili.com/read/cv17521097</a></p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/866300","replies":101,"created_ts":1657845550,"created":"08:39:10","title":"如何看待 2021.07.13 B 站崩溃事件","author":"Stendan","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/Stendan","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/f9de90ec72bec48eda14ec2131b181f8?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":866339,"node":"Apple","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/apple","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_mini.png?m=1630643913","description":"<p>大家现在用 MacBook 都是怎么办公的哟</p>\n<ul>\n<li>有没有外接显示器，有的话是什么型号</li>\n<li>有没有键盘、鼠标这些外设，分别啥型号</li>\n<li>是双屏还是盒盖使用单屏</li>\n</ul>\n<p>大家一起交流交流😊</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/866339","replies":89,"created_ts":1657852445,"created":"10:34:05","title":"MacBook 办公方式","author":"KevinXC","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/KevinXC","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/c0b9/45d0/552046_mini.png?m=1657852203"},{"id":866398,"node":"程序员","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1656605007","description":"<p>🐣初衷\n创建本群目的就是聚集一群 Gopher 和对 go 有兴趣的有志青年，帮助大家一同成长，希望加入到这个群里的每个人都能有所收获。</p>\n<p>👬入群须知\n这个群的目的就现在技术群确实不少，我也加了一些，但很多即使有技术碰撞，也都止于短暂的聊天，很快就被淹没。群内经常发言的也就几个活跃的人，大部分人都是默默的偶尔翻翻群消息，或者干脆静音不管了。这样其实也就失去了这个群的意义，我理想中的群应该像是一个班级，大家在一起学习，你不必跟所有人都有联系，甚至你只做好你自己，偶尔群里瞅两眼都行。</p>\n<p>💾群内学习\n1 、分享优秀文章，书籍，当然如果你能说出为什么推荐他就更好了。\n2 、平常开发中遇到的有趣的 bug 及解题步骤的分享。\n3 、提问题，提问题时最好自己已经做过尝试但仍未解决，并描述清楚出现问题的情况。优秀的问题即使没人解答也会记下来，组织成一个题库，待有兴趣的人可以进入题库尝试作答。</p>\n<p>💫注意点\n为了增加群内活跃度，本群达到一定人数会关闭入群通道\n本群不支持任何广告推广</p>\n<p>🎭 一个人走的很快，一群人可以走的很远，欢迎入群交流。\n有兴趣的可以联系 RmVZb3VuZ3M=</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/866398","replies":79,"created_ts":1657861567,"created":"13:06:07","title":"Go 友会继续招纳(之前小伙伴加入没来得及处理)","author":"fy1206","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/fy1206","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/aecd/00dc/535964_mini.png?m=1655347575"},{"id":866406,"node":"分享创造","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/create","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/70ef/df2e/17_mini.png?m=1650095309","description":"<p>经过三个月的 TF 测试（<a href=\"https://v2ex.com/t/848300?p=2\" rel=\"nofollow\">我开发了一个用于播放 m3u8 文件的 App ，已上架 TF ，欢迎测试👏🏻</a>），APTV 终于上架 AppStore 了，国区售价 12 元，美区售价 1.99 刀，支持 iOS 、iPadOS 、tvOS （已上 Testflight ）、macOS （已建好文件夹）</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>有 tvOS 需求建议从美区入</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"https://apps.apple.com/cn/app/aptv/id1630403500\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"Download from AppStore\" class=\"embedded_image\" 